    public class ProfessionalClaim
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR ProfessionalClaim Resource (ProfessionalClaim)

    Definition: A provider issued list of services and products provided, or to be provided, to a patient which is provided to an insurer for payment recovery.

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/ProfessionalClaim
